<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>132</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bù guǎn duō shǎo qū rǔ, bù guǎn duō shǎo mó nán, wǒ men cóng méi yǒu wèi jù guò tiāo zhàn,
 ràng bù biàn de xìn niàn huà zuò nà shèng huǒ wǒ men yào wǒ men yào bǎ fú yīn zhī huǒ diǎn rán,
 zài dà de fēng yǔ wǒ men tóng zǒu guò, zài dà de kǔ nán wǒ men tóng áo guò,
 xīn líng xiāng tōng bù yào shuō shén me xiàng qián zǒu xiàng qián zǒu yǒng yuǎn yě bù huì cuò,
 bǎi xìng kùn kǔ zài hēi àn de jiǎo luò, wú shù shuāng kě wàng de yǎn jīng qī dài zhe nǐ wǒ
 shén shèng de shǐ mìng, yī qǐ dān qǐ lái liú lèi qù sā zhǒng bì huān hū shōu gē.</lyrics>
<title>xiàng qián zǒu yǒng yuǎn bù huì cuò 迦南132</title>
</song>